paragraphs.title: Load All Audit Results
paragraphs.text:
%spark.r
all <- data.frame(group = character(0), run = character(0), suite = character(0), case = character(0), pass = character(0), trace = character(0))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/1-master/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/discipline/fault-management/validate-fault-management-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('fault_management')
tmp$run <- as.factor('before')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/1-master/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/discipline/fse/validate-fse-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('fse')
tmp$run <- as.factor('before')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/1-master/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/discipline/vandv/validate-vandv-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('vandv')
tmp$run <- as.factor('before')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/1-master/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/foundation/analysis/validate-analysis-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('analysis')
tmp$run <- as.factor('before')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))

tmp$run <- as.factor('before')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))

all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))

tmp$run <- as.factor('before')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/3-owl/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/discipline/fault-management/validate-fault-management-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('fault_management')
tmp$run <- as.factor('after')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/3-owl/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/discipline/fse/validate-fse-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('fse')
tmp$run <- as.factor('after')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/3-owl/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/discipline/vandv/validate-vandv-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('vandv')
tmp$run <- as.factor('after')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))

all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/3-owl/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/foundation/mission/validate-mission-group.csv')
tmp$group <- as.factor('mission')
tmp$run <- as.factor('after')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
tmp <- read.csv('/tmp/conversion-test/3-owl/tests/imce.jpl.nasa.gov/foundation/owl2-mof2/validate-owl2-mof2-group.csv')

tmp$run <- as.factor('after')

tmp$group <- as.factor('Metrology')
tmp$run <- as.factor('after')
all <- data.frame(rbind(all, tmp))
remove(tmp)

suites <- levels(all$suite)
suites

paragraphs.title: Before/After Comparison Detail for All Groups
paragraphs.text:
%spark.r
cases <- function(frame, run, pass) frame[which(frame$run == run & frame$pass == pass),]$case
pass.before.cases <- function(frame) cases(frame, "before", T)
pass.after.cases <- function(frame) cases(frame, "after", T)
fail.before.cases <- function(frame) cases(frame, "before", F)
fail.after.cases <- function(frame) cases(frame, "after", F)
analyze.cases <- function(frame, group, suite) {
    tmp <- frame[which(frame$group == group & frame$suite == suite),c("run", "case", "pass")]
    p.b.c <- pass.before.cases(tmp)
    p.a.c <- pass.after.cases(tmp)
    f.b.c <- fail.before.cases(tmp)
    f.a.c <- fail.after.cases(tmp)
    p.b.a <- setdiff(p.b.c, p.a.c)
    p.a.b <- setdiff(p.a.c, p.b.c)
    f.b.a <- setdiff(f.b.c, f.a.c)
    f.a.b <- setdiff(f.a.c, f.b.c)
    list(
        pass.before.not.after = p.b.a,
        pass.after.not.before = p.a.b,
        fail.before.not.after = f.b.a,
        fail.after.not.before = f.a.b
    )        
}
analyze.suites <- function(frame, group) {
    suites <- levels(frame$suite)
    l <- lapply(suites, function(suite) analyze.cases(all, group, suite))    
    names(l) <- suites
    l
}
analyze.groups <- function(frame) {
    groups = levels(frame$group)
    l <- lapply(groups, function(group) analyze.suites(frame, group))
    names(l) <- groups
    l
}
analyze.groups(all)
